English:
@q0 @d0This may sound a bit strange, but we urgently need fish guts - or rather a certain parasite that infests the local fish shoals in the <color=#ffffff>deep waters</color>. The parasite itself is harmless, but if you ferment and process it, you get an effective poison which we like to use for silent arrow hunting.

Can you get us some of this <color=#ffffff>fish parasite</color> (x3)? 

If you accept, I will also provide you with a suitable <color=#fbff00>underwater hunting crossbow</color> for this purpose. Note that you cannot hold the weapon and swim at the same time!

