English:
@d0 @q0The Survival Tool has three working modes that you can set with a <color=#44ff00>right mouse</color> click: <color=#ffffff>Defense</color>, <color=#ffffff>Resource </color>and <color=#ffffff>Salvage</color>. 

The <u>Resource mode</u> is especially important! Use it to gather <color=#ffffff>wood</color> from trees and <color=#ffffff>carbon</color> from resource rocks <u>early on</u> to <color=#ffffff>build your first shelter</color> as soon as possible! You can also use it to destroy plants, stones and other obstacles that are in your way or prevent you from picking something up! 

Would you like to see a more detailed video about the Survival Tool and its working modes?

Chinese (simplified):
@d0 @q0 生存工具有三种工作模式，你可以通过<color=#44ff00>右键点击</color>来设置：<color=#ffffff>防御</color>、<color=#ffffff>资源 </color>和<color=#ffffff>回收</color>。 

<u>资源模式</u>尤其重要！用它从树木中收集<color=#ffffff>木头</color>，从资源岩石中收集<color=#ffffff>碳</color>，<u>尽早</u>建造你的第一座庇护所！你也可以使用它来摧毁挡在你的路上的植物、石头和其他障碍物，或者阻止你捡起某样东西！ 

