English:
@d0 @q0<color=#00ffff>Ownership = Control!</color> 
When the core is destroyed, all devices, defenses, doors etc. will stop working until you control the base by placing your own core.

Once you own the base, you will be able to access and control all of the base's functions through the control panel (P). Even turrets and other defenses will then work in your favor!

@p9 @d0 @q0<color=#00ffff>Ownership = More efficient looting!</color>

If you're in the mood for a loot spree, you can use the logistics function (F4) to empty containers faster and easier.

@p9 @d0 @q0<color=#00ffff>Ownership = More efficient building ... and salvaging.</color>

If you own the base, you <color=#ffffff>get back ALL components </color>when you dismantle building blocks and devices - and you don't lose anything, no matter what type or quality of dismantling tool you are using! @w2 <u>In addition:</u> if you already have a <color=#ffffff>Multi Tool</color> unlocked in the Tech Tree (<color=#44ff00>F3</color>), you can even <color=#ffffff>get back complete bricks and devices </color>with the RETRIEVE BLOCKS setting! If you find a rare device or turret, this approach is the only way you can use it for yourself!

Chinese (simplified):
@d0 @q0 <color=#00ffff>拥有权 = 控制权！</color> 
当核心被摧毁时，所有设备、防御、门等将停止工作，直到你通过放置自己的核心来接管基地。

一旦你拥有基地，你将能够通过控制面板（P）访问和控制基地的所有功能。即使是炮塔和其他防御也会为你工作！

@p9 @d0 @q0 <color=#00ffff>拥有权 = 更高效的掠夺！</color>

如果你想进行掠夺狂欢，你可以使用物流功能（F4）更快更容易地清空容器。

@p9 @d0 @q0 <color=#00ffff>拥有权 = 更高效的建造 </color>

如果你拥有基地，并且你已经在科技树（<color=#44ff00>F3</color>）中解锁了<color=#ffffff>多功能工具</color>，你可以使用 拆卸模式<color=#ffffff>回收完整的方块和设备</color>！如果你找到了稀有的设备或炮塔，这种方法是你唯一可以使用它的方式！

