English:
@q0 @d0 To build a <color=#ffffff>Hover Vessel</color> only a few steps are necessary.  In this tutorial i will show you how to get a quick result with the help of the <color=#ffffff>Blueprint Libary</color> (<color=#44ff00>F2</color>) by using a <color=#ffffff>FRAME</color>.

We will then equip this frame with the necessary functional parts.

Note: The FRAME is marked with <color=#ffffff>NUMBERS</color> that indicate the <u>necessary parts, their position</u> and a suggested (!) <u>installation sequence</u>!

Chinese (simplified):
@q0 @d0 建造一个 <color=#ffffff>悬浮飞船</color> 只需要几个步骤。在这个教程中，我将向你展示如何通过使用 <color=#ffffff>蓝图库</color>（<color=#44ff00>F2</color>）中的一个 <color=#ffffff>框架</color> 来快速获得结果。

然后我们将为这个框架装备必要的功能部件。

注意：框架上标有 <color=#ffffff>数字</color>，这些数字表示 <u>必要的部件，它们的位置</u>，以及建议的（！）<u>安装顺序</u>！

English:
@q0 @d0Open the Blueprint Libary (<color=#44ff00>F2</color>). Select the tab '<color=#ffffff>PREFABS</color>' on the left side <color=#00ffff>( 1 )</color>. Set the filter '<color=#ffffff>Base</color>' <color=#00ffff>( 2 )</color>. Enter the word '<color=#ffffff>Frame</color>' in the search field <color=#00ffff>( 3 )</color>. Select one of the FRAMEs <u>you have the materials for</u> and click the '<color=#ffffff>TO FACTORY</color>' <color=#00ffff>( 4 )</color> button on the <color=#ffffff>lower right</color> screen.

In the new window, drag all materials, for example the <color=#ffffff>Wood Planks</color> from your inventory into the '<color=#ffffff>INTAKE</color>' box <color=#00ffff>( 5 )</color>. When all requirements are <color=#44ff00>GREEN</color> <color=#00ffff>( 6 )</color>, press <color=#ffffff>START PRODUCTION</color> <color=#00ffff>( 7 )</color>. 
The crafting will take a few minutes. You can close the window. As soon as the production is <color=#ffffff>complete</color> you will get a <color=#ffffff>notification on your screen</color>!

Chinese (simplified):
@q0 @d0 打开蓝图库（<color=#44ff00>F2</color>）。在左侧选择 '<color=#ffffff>预制件</color>' 标签页 <color=#00ffff>( 1 )</color>。设置过滤器 '<color=#ffffff>基地</color>' <color=#00ffff>( 2 )</color>。在搜索字段中输入 '<color=#ffffff>框架</color>' <color=#00ffff>( 3 )</color>。选择一个 <u>你有材料的</u> FRAME 并点击 <color=#ffffff>右下屏幕</color> 的 '<color=#ffffff>添加到工厂</color>' <color=#00ffff>( 4 )</color> 按钮。

在新窗口中，将所有材料，例如，将你的库存中的 <color=#ffffff>木板</color> 拖入 '<color=#ffffff>输入</color>' 框 <color=#00ffff>( 5 )</color>。当所有需求都是 <color=#44ff00>绿色</color> <color=#00ffff>( 6 )</color> 时，按下 <color=#ffffff>开始生产</color> <color=#00ffff>( 7 )</color>。

制作需要几分钟的时间。你可以关闭窗口。一旦生产 <color=#ffffff>完成</color>，你将在你的屏幕上收到一个 <color=#ffffff>通知</color>！

